title: Chumbawamba 1982-2000
description:
I found a couple of CDs of what I believe to be part of a special
somebody&#039;s FTP archive, downloaded in 2000. There was more, but
this is all I&#039;ve got. Cheers to the archive keeper!

The files were untagged, so I&#039;ve tagged them to the best of my
ability with great help from the Chumbawamba discography
available at various places on the interwebs. Cheers to the
discography keeper! (All mistakes in the tags are mine.)

Enjoy!
